tafsir[30]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juu…óe Mum on tun mawnii O …óuu…óii mo∆ī∆īere Alla nde, ko Kanko woni hattan…óo kala huunde. Alaa ko ronkiŇčta Mo."
  67,2,"On tagir…óo maayde e nguurdam, fii ndaarndagol on onon …ďee yim…ďe, annda ko hommbo e mo'on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude golle. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, Haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  67,3,"O tagu…óo kammuuli jee…ói…ói, kammu kala hino dewtii e hoore nguya ko aldaa e momondirgol hakkunde majji. An ndaaroowo on, a yi'ataa e ko …ďuradata woo e tagu Allah ngun. Yiltii gite maa …óen ndaaraa. Taw si a yi'ay ceekol maa …ďurdal? Pellet, a yi'ataa …óum ! Ko yi'aa, ko tagu √Īe√Īaangu, gollii ngu."
  67,4,"Refti ruttitin ndaar…óe maa …óen laa…ďi …ói…ói, gite …óen ruttitoray e maa…óa hara ko …óe hoy…óe, tawde …óe yi'ataa ella ma Ňčakkere e tagugol kammu ngun, hara kadi ko …óe ta∆īii…óe e ndaarugol."
  67,5,"Gom…óii Men cu…óirii kammu ngu aduna ngun koode jalbu…óe, Men wa…ói …óen koode fi…óir…óe seytanuuji wujjay…ói he…óoo …óin ko sunna …ói, Men hebilani …ďe ka laakara ton lette Yiite Hu…ď…ďunge."
  67,6,"√Ďalnde Darngal, hino woodani …ďen yeddu…ďe Joomi mun, lette Yiite Jahnnama. Nge bonii ruttorde jaa∆īoytee…ďe e magge."
  67,7,"Si wonii …ďe bugaama ka nder Yiite, …ďe naniraynge hito kaanungo sanne, hara hinge fatira wa ko wulnata."
  67,8,"Hinge e…ď…ďa fultagol, nge sennditoo, hakkee ko nge tikkani naadaa…óo e magge …ďen. Tuma kala nde fedde e heefer…ďe …ďen bugaa e magge, Malaa'ikaa…ďe ayninaa…ďe nge …ďen lamndoo …ďe wi'a: Enee ! Nulaa…óo araano e mon aduna, jertinaynoo…óo on e lette Allah …óen?"
  67,9,"Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'a : Ko pellet, Nulaa…óo aruno e amen tigi, himo jertinaynoo men e lette Allah …óen, kono men fenni mo, men wi'i mo: Allah jippinaali hay wahayu. Onon …ďee Nulaa…ďe, on wonaali si wanaa e nder majjere mawnde wo…ó…óii goonga."
  67,10,"Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'ita : Si men nanayno men ja…ďa, maa hara men haqqilayno men senndindira hakkunde goonga e meere, men jeyetanooke e yim…ďe Yiite …ďen; men gom…óinayno Nulaa…ďe …ďen, men goongina ko …ďe addi kon, fii no men jeyiree e yim…ďe Aljanna …ďen."
  67,11,"∆Āe qirritanoo ko'e-ma…ď…ďe, keeferaaku e fennugol …ďe ngol, Yiite ngen jojji e ma…ď…ďe. Awa halakuyee woodanii yim…ďe Yiite …ďen."
  67,12,"Pellet, huloo…ďe Joomi mun …ďen ka …ďe weeyata …óon, hino woodani …ďen haforaneede junuubi, e njo…ďdi mawndi ndiin woni Aljanna."
  67,13,"Suu…óee onon …ďee yim…ďe, konngu…ói mon maa fe√Ī√Īinon …ói. Allah kan hino anndi fii majji. Kanko senii…óo On, himo anndi ko woni e …ďer…óe jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Huunde e …óum suu…óaaki Mo."
  67,14,"E hara tagu…óo taguuli …óin fof On anndaa sirru e ko …ďuri sirru wirnaade? Ko Kanko le woni Newanii…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Humpitii…óo fiyakuuji ma…ď…ďe. Huunde suu…óaaki Mo e …óin."
  67,15,"Ko Kanko wa…óani on leydi ndin eltaandi newiniraa ka ho…óee : haray yahee e seraaji mayri, √Īaamon e arsike Makko mo O hebilani on e mayri. Ko ka Makko tun woni ummital fii √Īaaweede njo…ďdi."
  67,16,"E on hooli wonnde Allah won…óo On ka kammu nde fettinta leydi e mo'on leydi ndin wano O mutiniri Qaaruuna e mayri? Hari le ko ndi newinanoondi fii ho…óugol e mun. Tawaa yoo hindi dilla e mon …ďaawo ndi dee∆īude."
  67,17,"Kaa on hooli wonnde Allah won…óo ka kammu On nde O accitataa kaa∆īe e mo'on immorde ka kammu, wano O accitirnoo …óen e yim…ďe Luutu …ďen? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jertinaango Am ngon, tuma yi'oton lette Am …óen. Ko woni tun, on nafitoroytaa …óum …ďaawo nde yi'oyton lette …óen."
  67,18,"Sellii wonnde mofte adinoo…ďe …ďen sirkoo…ďe …óon …ďen fenniino, lette Allah …óen yani e ma…ď…ďe fewndo …ďe ha…ď…ďitinoo e yeddugol fenna. Taskii ko honno lette Am …óen wattinirnoo e ma…ď…ďe ! ∆äum wonuno lette sattu…óe."
  67,19,"E …ďee fennoo…ďe yi'aali colli …óin dow ma…ď…ďe, tuma …ói wiirata, …ói fontay gabitannji majji …óin e henndu ndun, …ói √Īobba …ói kadi? Wonnde ko Allah jogitii …óin fii wata …ói yanu ka leydi. Pellet, Kanko ko O reenu…óo kala huunde. Hay huunde suu…óaaki Mo."
  67,20,"Konuujo alanaa on onon …ďee heefer…ďe …ďe, mo no da…óana on e lette Allah …óen tuma O faandanii on …óe. Tigi on, heefer…ďe …ďen wonaali si wanaa hodaa…ďe; ko seytaane hodi …ďe, …ďe …óaynitori mo."
  67,21,"Alaa arsikoowo on si Allah jogitike ko O arsikata on kon. Si ko woni, heefer…ďe …ďen duumi e ∆īaggere e townitaare, e salagol goonga."
  67,22,"Kere ko on yaaroowo no hippi yeeso mun, e maanaa sirkoowo on …ďuri feewude? Kaa ko gom…óin…óo yahoowo on no √Īii…ďi e laawol focciingol?"
  67,23,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe fennoo…ďe : ko Allah woni tagu…óo on, O wa…óani on nan…óe …óe naniron, e gii…óe e yi'iron, e …ďer…óe …óe haqqiliron. Kono fan…óii ko yettoton Mo e ko O neeminiri on kon."
  67,24,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe fennoo…ďe : Ko Allah woni saakit…óo on e leydi ndin, wanaa sanamuuji mon …ói tagataa …óin hay fus ! Kadi, ko ka Makko tun woni moo…ďitoyte…óon √Ďalnde Darngal, fii √Īaaweede yo…ďitee, wanaa ka sanamuuji mon. Hulee Mo kisan, rewon Mo Kanko tun."
  67,25,"∆Āee fennoo…ďe ummital no wi'a : ko honnde tuma woni fii ndee fodoore nde fodu-…óaa men an Muhammadu e wonndii…ďe maa …ďen, si tawii ko on goongu…ďe e kon nodditi…óon wi'ugol nde aray?"
  67,26,"Maakan …ďe yo Nulaa…óo : Anndee anndugol fii Darngal, ko ka Allah woni. Hay gooto anndaa nde ngal darotoo si wanaa Kanko. Min on ko mi jertiniinoowo tun …ďannginana on jertinaango am."
  67,27,"Nde kammbaa on yanoyta e ma…ď…ďe …ďe yi'a lette …óen ka …ďadii …ďe, woni √Ďalnde Darngal, geece yeddu…ďe Allah …ďen wayloto …ďawla, …ďe wi'anee ontuma : ko …óum …óoo woni …óa…ď…ďayno…óon yaccinaneede ka aduna."
  67,28,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe fennoo…ďe : Yeetee lam, si Allah ∆īettiti lam, O ∆īettitii gom…óim…ďe wonndu…ďe e am …ďen, wollo O yurmii min ko hommbo da…óndata heefer…ďe …ďen e lette muusu…óe? O alaa da…óndoo- wo mbo e he…óe hay gooto."
  67,29,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe : Ko Kanko Jom hinaraŇčke noddoowo on e rewugol Mo Kanko tun On. Men gom…óinii Mo, ko e Makko tun kadi woni ko men fawata fiyakuuji amen. Aray pellet, nde anndoton, ko hommbo wonunoo e majjere …ďanngunde e wonunoo…ďe e laawol focciingol ngol."
  67,30,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe : Yeetee lam, si ndiyam …óam yaroton …óam wattinii …ďee…ďu…óam ka leydi, ko hommbo addanta on ontuma ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam ko ila? Ko Allah tun."
